* Duane Wessels, &quot;Web Caching&quot; (O&#x27;Reilly and Associates, 2001). 
* Michael Rabinovich and Oliver Spatschak, &quot;Web Caching and Replication&quot; (Addison Wesley, 2001). </text><links>
