==Maximum likelihood parameter estimation==
Given &quot;k&quot; matrices, each of size &quot;n&quot; × &quot;p&quot;, denoted formula_37, which we assume have been sampled i.i.d. from a matrix normal distribution, the maximum likelihood estimate of the parameters can be obtained by maximizing:
