:formula_42

==Drawing values from the distribution==
Sampling from the matrix normal distribution is a special case of the sampling procedure for the multivariate normal distribution. Let formula_29 be an &quot;n&quot; by &quot;p&quot; matrix of &quot;np&quot; independent samples from the standard normal distribution, so that
